title: Josh Hagquist from The Beautiful Mistake
itunes:title: Josh Hagquist from The Beautiful Mistake
description:
Welcome to this weeks chat with my good friend, Josh Hagquist from The Beautiful Mistake! We get into the history of the band, his life being a trumpet player and ego. We really pick apart so many topics that don't typically get covered in this show, so I really hope you enjoy it. They have a new EP out on Wiretap Records in March of 2020. Check out Great American Ghost and their new track, "Prison Of Hate" on Spotify. Their new LP is out now! Visit Rockabilia and use the code PC100WORDS for 15% off of your order. The best place for all of your VIP experiences at shows is with Soundrink. 

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
